descriptionHtml:
This App gives access to our digital market research panel. We offer the opportunity to participate in surveys getting real-time information on various topics and sharing your opinion to our Marketagent.com - community. Marketagent.com is an online research panel platform existing since 2000. We offer to our panelists the possibility to participate in online research surveys and earn bonuspoints that can be exchanged to various incentives.

creator: Marketagent.com online reSEARCH GmbH
descriptionHtml: Take the opportunity now and actively shape future products and services with your opinion. Simply take part in Marketagent's online surveys and determine the trends of tomorrow. For each participation, you receive monetary bonus points that you can exchange for cash or products from our cooperation partners. In our app, there are also many other ways in which you can improve your bonus points account. Your participation is absolutely free of charge and you have no obligations. If you don't feel like taking part, that's no problem, because the next online survey is sure to come around. Of course, your data is in safe hands with us.     Do it like our 2.3 million members around the globe and become part of our Marketagent Community. Your opinion counts and pays off!    - Register for free at Marketagent  - Take part in our online surveys  - Receive monetary bonus points for each participation  - The payout takes place within a few days  - Become part of our community with more than 2.3 million members    If you have questions or a problem, our support team is available at info@marketagent.com and looks forward to your feedback.
